<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: blinding -->
  <BlindingCeremony.label>除目</BlindingCeremony.label>
  <!-- EN: A cutter will ritualistically blind a target. The audience will watch as the cutter gives a speech, cuts out both of the target's eyes, and says some closing words. The target will be left bleeding and need immediate medical care. -->
  <BlindingCeremony.description>除目師替受禮者摒棄雙目。觀禮人會在旁參與，除目師會進行佈道、移除受禮者的雙目、並致詞作結。受禮者事成後會流血並需要即時醫療照顧。</BlindingCeremony.description>
  
  <!-- EN: conversion ritual -->
  <Conversion.label>傳教佈道</Conversion.label>
  <!-- EN: Try to persuade someone into joining your ideoligion. -->
  <Conversion.description>試著說服某人加入你的理念。</Conversion.description>
  
  <!-- EN: christmas tree party -->
  <DateRitualConsumable.label>聖誕樹派對</DateRitualConsumable.label>
  <!-- EN: A celebratory gathering for your colonists to have fun. A leader will give an encouraging speech, then everyone will socialize for a while. -->
  <DateRitualConsumable.description>一場讓你的居民享樂的慶祝聚會。領袖會以鼓勵演講起頭，然後大家將一起聊天玩樂。</DateRitualConsumable.description>
  
  <!-- EN: public execution -->
  <Execution.label>公開處決</Execution.label>
  <!-- EN: An executioner will publicly execute a prisoner. The executioner will give a short speech, execute the prisoner by cutting, and say some closing words. Spectating slaves will become afraid and intimidated, and colonists will feel exhilarated or disgusted depending on their beliefs. -->
  <Execution.description>劊子手將公開處決一名俘虜。劊子手會進行簡短演講，然後對俘虜處刑，並致詞作結。參與的奴隸將會變得害怕和恐懼，而居民會視乎信仰感到高興或反感。</Execution.description>
  <!-- EN: Public execution -->
  <Execution.tipLabelOverride>公開處決</Execution.tipLabelOverride>
  
  <!-- EN: social festival -->
  <Festival.label>社交節日</Festival.label>
  <!-- EN: A celebratory gathering for your colonists to have fun. A leader will give an encouraging speech, then everyone will socialize for a while. -->
  <Festival.description>一場讓你的居民享樂的慶祝聚會。領袖會以鼓勵演講起頭，然後大家將一起聊天玩樂。</Festival.description>
  
  <!-- EN: funeral -->
  <Funeral.label>喪禮</Funeral.label>
  <!-- EN: A gathering that occurs around a believer's grave after they die and are buried. If the body is destroyed, an empty grave can be used. Slaves don't get funerals. -->
  <Funeral.description>一場圍繞在逝世信徒墓前的集會。如果屍首無蹤，人們將會聚在衣冠冢前。奴隸不會有喪禮。</Funeral.description>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} should be buried and given a funeral so {PAWN_possessive} friends and family can say farewell. -->
  <Funeral.extraTextPawnDeathLetter>{PAWN_nameDef}應該要被埋葬並舉行一場喪禮，使{PAWN_possessive}朋友和家人可以道別。</Funeral.extraTextPawnDeathLetter>
  
  <!-- EN: funeral (no corpse) -->
  <FuneralNoCorpse.label>喪禮(衣冠冢)</FuneralNoCorpse.label>
  <!-- EN: A gathering that occurs around a believer's grave after they die and are buried. If the body is destroyed, an empty grave can be used. Slaves don't get funerals. -->
  <FuneralNoCorpse.description>一場圍繞在逝世信徒墓前的集會。如果屍首無蹤，人們將會聚在衣冠冢前。奴隸不會有喪禮。</FuneralNoCorpse.description>
  
  <!-- EN: gladiator duel -->
  <GladiatorDuel.label>角鬥比試</GladiatorDuel.label>
  <!-- EN: A duel between prisoners or slaves. The organizer will give a speech to excite the crowd, then the duelists will fight until one of them falls or time runs out. If weapons are in the arena, the duelists will pick up and use them. -->
  <GladiatorDuel.description>一場俘虜或奴隸間的比試。主辦者將進行演講帶動觀眾的高漲情緒，然後角鬥士將會毆鬥直至其中一方倒下或時限結束。如果場上有武器，角鬥士將會撿起使用。</GladiatorDuel.description>
  <!-- EN: Prisoner/slave gladiator duel -->
  <GladiatorDuel.tipLabelOverride>俘虜/奴隸角鬥比試</GladiatorDuel.tipLabelOverride>
  
  <!-- EN: leader speech -->
  <LeaderSpeech.label>領袖演講</LeaderSpeech.label>
  <!-- EN: A rousing speech intended to improve morale. Colonists will gather, and the leader will speak for a few hours. If all goes well, listeners will feel inspired, and gain respect for the leader. If it goes poorly, the speech will do social damage. -->
  <LeaderSpeech.description>一場激勵士氣的振奮演講。居民會聚集聆聽領袖發言數小時。如果演講得宜，聽眾會感到啟發，並對領袖更加尊敬。但如果發言不當，這場演講將會損害社交。</LeaderSpeech.description>
  
